  "texts": [
    "Failure Knowledge GraphHara et al. [2] employed text mining techniques based on syntactic analysis, including the extraction of co-occurrence and dependency relations, as well as causal relation extraction using the algorithm proposed by Sakaji et al [7].",
    "They constructed failure KG, a knowledge graph of failure information.",
    "A portion of failure KG is shown in Fig. 1.",
    "Failure KG [2].",
    "This figure illustrates the nodes related to the clutch node."
  ]
}